yle=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\">\r\n		<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-right: 4.3pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:24pt;\">\r\n			<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8e267e90-7fff-777f-5734-317f383669c9\"><span background-color:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\">Al-quran&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol start=\"3\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;\">\r\n	<li background-color:=\"\" color:=\"\" dir=\"ltr\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" margin-left:=\"\" roboto=\"\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\">\r\n		<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.88;margin-right: 4.3pt;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14.5pt;\">\r\n			<span style=\"color:#4d080c;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8e267e90-7fff-777f-5734-317f383669c9\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Pakaian tradisional</span></span></span></h4>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-right: 4.3pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:24pt;\">\r\n	<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8e267e90-7fff-777f-5734-317f383669c9\"><span background-color:=\"\" color:=\"\" font-variant-east-asian:=\"\" font-variant-numeric:=\"\" helvetica=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \" vertical-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\">Setiap adat memiliki pakaian tradisional, tidak terkecuali adat Sunda yang umumnya banyak kita jumpai di Jawa Barat. Di samping membawa perhiasan dan perlengkapan ibadah, calon mempelai pria juga biasanya menyertakan pakaian tradisional berupa baju kebaya atau kain batik. Jenis kebaya yang dipilih bisa t